      Addition:_msgid=<msgid>_userid=<userID>:<locationName>-<locationDescription>_(<longitude>,<latitude>)

      Underscore indicates a space. You must follow the spacing, etc. precisely. longitude/latitude must be rounded.

      For example

      Addition: msgid=253 101:Stadium-Champions (75,-65)
